"    // println!(\"Pierwszy element vec2 to: {}\", vec2[0]);\n"
"    // println!(\"vec2 len: {}\", vec2.len());\n"
"    // TODO: uncomment two lines above and see compiler errors.\n"

#: src/fn/closures/closure_examples/iter_any.md:44
